definition.text: TensorFlow.js support multiple different backends that implement tensor storage and mathematical operations. At any given time, only one backend is active. Most of the time, TensorFlow.js will automatically choose the best backend for you given the current Execution Environmet.

paragraphs.text: Left click and Edit to enter edit mode and change this text. ENTER to write new paragraphs. ESC to exit edit mode. Then you can use docs.save to save your changes and app.contribute to send it to the main repository.
